<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/37817963" target="_blank" data-id="7334461" data-za-element-name="Title">
如何看待 Wordpress 的新项目 Calypso 将改用 Node.js + React 重写？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/37817963/answer/77240423">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="26321658">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="77240423"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>169</a>
</div>

