<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/32039257" target="_blank" data-id="5015093" data-za-element-name="Title">
你是怎么看完《JavaScript权威指南》《JavaScript高级程序设计》等这类厚书的？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/32039257/answer/73049906">
