<div class="zm-item-rich-text expandable js-collapse-body" data-resourceid="10989500" data-action="/answer/content" data-author-name="路人甲" data-entry-url="/question/46939006/answer/104211095">

<textarea hidden class="content">我这里不是推荐网站，只是对网站的知识进行梳理。&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;如果你是it从业者，或是想学习编程？&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;点这里，丰富的学习路线以及浅显易懂的教程帮你一步一步跨进it殿堂：&lt;a href=&quot;https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/passer&quot; class=&quot;internal&quot;&gt;学习编程 - 知乎专栏&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;当然如果你想了解我或者联系我：&lt;a class=&quot;internal&quot; href=&quot;https://www.zhihu.com/people/lu-ren-jia-84-27&quot;&gt;路人甲&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;如果你刚刚入门？&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;1、&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;如果你想系统的学习&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a class=&quot; wrap external&quot; href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//study.163.com/course/introduction/1002904008.htm%23/courseDetail&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;HTML 5全套课程精讲（HTML5+CSS3）&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//study.163.com/course/introduction/171001.htm%23/courseDetail&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;HTML5入门 - 网易云课堂&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//study.163.com/course/introduction/273013.htm%23/courseDetail&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;零基础学HTML语言&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//study.163.com/course/introduction/245007.htm%23/courseDetail&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;Web开发入门 - 网易云课堂&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a class=&quot; wrap external&quot; href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//study.163.com/course/introduction/267002.htm%23/courseDetail&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;HTML5视频教程&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//study.163.com/course/introduction/318008.htm%23/courseDetail&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;CSS+DIV初级基础&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//study.163.com/course/introduction/266008.htm%23/courseDetail&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;oeasy教html、css网页设计与制作(html5教程)&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;2、&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;如果你想快速入门&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a class=&quot; wrap external&quot; href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//study.163.com/course/introduction/999036.htm%23/courseDetail&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;HTML5+CSS3快速入门&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a class=&quot; wrap external&quot; href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//study.163.com/course/introduction/432008.htm%23/courseDetail&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;8小时学会HTML网页开发&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//study.163.com/course/introduction/215009.htm%23/courseDetail&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;轻松学习网页设计系列视频教程&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;如果你有了一定基础&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a class=&quot; wrap external&quot; href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//study.163.com/course/introduction/705111.htm%23/courseDetail&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;[云知梦]CSS样式设计&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a class=&quot; wrap external&quot; href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//study.163.com/course/introduction/554002.htm%23/courseDetail&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;PHPChina学院CSS3 疯狂5小时&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//study.163.com/course/introduction/1492002.htm%23/courseDetail&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;JavaScript开发详解&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a class=&quot; wrap external&quot; href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//study.163.com/course/introduction/265013.htm%23/courseDetail&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;JavaScript - 网易云课堂&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a class=&quot; wrap external&quot; href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//study.163.com/course/introduction/195001.htm%23/courseDetail&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;JavaScript - 网易云课堂&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//study.163.com/course/introduction/224014.htm%23/courseDetail&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;精通JavaScript开发&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//mooc.study.163.com/learn/NEU-1000086001%3Ftid%3D1000117001%23/learn/content&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;Javascript_入门&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;如果以上你都学完了&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//study.163.com/course/introduction/717031.htm%23/courseDetail&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;HTML5前端开发实战&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//study.163.com/course/introduction/650003.htm%23/courseDetail&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;珠峰培训JS前端实战项目:动画与日历&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//study.163.com/course/introduction/1311001.htm%23/courseDetail&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;网页前端制作及PHP网站搭建课程&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;最后如果你很懒可以选择这个：&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.jikexueyuan.com/course/web/&quot; class=&quot; external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;http://www.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;visible&quot;&gt;jikexueyuan.com/course/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;web/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ellipsis&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img data-rawheight=&quot;412&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;617&quot; src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/87c120d4673b8bbc5513f95dc10d3ca7_b.png&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;617&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/87c120d4673b8bbc5513f95dc10d3ca7_r.png&quot;&gt;</textarea>


<div class="zh-summary summary clearfix">
<img data-rawheight="412" data-rawwidth="617" src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/87c120d4673b8bbc5513f95dc10d3ca7_200x112.png" class="origin_image inline-img zh-lightbox-thumb" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/87c120d4673b8bbc5513f95dc10d3ca7_r.png">
我这里不是推荐网站，只是对网站的知识进行梳理。 <b>如果你是it从业者，或是想学习编程？</b><b>点这里，丰富的学习路线以及浅显易懂的教程帮你一步一步跨进it殿堂：<a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/passer" class="internal">学习编程 - 知乎专栏</a></b><b>当然如果你想了解我或者联系我：<a class="internal" href="https://www.zhihu.com/people/lu-ren-jia-84-27">路人甲</a></b> <b>如果你刚刚入门？</b> <b>1、</b><b>如果你想系统的学习</b> <a class=" wrap external" href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//study.163.com/course/introduction/1002904008.htm%23/courseDetail" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">…<i class="icon-external"></i></a>

