<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/41560189" target="_blank" data-id="8831437" data-za-element-name="Title">
参加第二届前端开发者年度大会是个什么样的体验？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/41560189/answer/91483261">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="32031064">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="91483261"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>167</a>
</div>

