<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/20269059" target="_blank" data-id="287803" data-za-element-name="Title">
移动前端开发和 Web 前端开发的区别是什么？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/20269059/answer/21502610">
