<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/39659757" target="_blank" data-id="8071357" data-za-element-name="Title">
如何评价阿当的文章《当我说前端基础时，我在说什么》？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/39659757/answer/82485924">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="28424122">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="82485924"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>165</a>
</div>

