<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/29848048" target="_blank" data-id="4121914" data-za-element-name="Title">
angular 和 React 想选择一个学习，哪个比较好？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/29848048/answer/45793588">
